Craft Focus		KEY:Craft Focus ~ Oracle	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	SOURCEPAGE:p.63	(Ex): As divination is an intimate act between ones body and soul, an oracle must prepare her own tools by spending 24 hours in meditation with the object she plans to use as her divination focus. The following day, she is exhausted (see special conditions for details on being exhausted) for 24 hours. Some examples of a divination focus are a metal bowl for holding water, a forked stick, rune stones, or a small silver mirror. If a focus is lost or destroyed, an oracle must create a new one before she may use her powers again.
Empower		KEY:Empower ~ Oracle		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.SpellLike		SOURCEPAGE:p.63																																																																																										(Sp): All variable, numeric effects of all divination abilities are increased by one-half. Saving throws and opposed rolls are not affected, nor are abilities without random variables.
Enlarge		KEY:Enlarge ~ Oracle		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.SpellLike		SOURCEPAGE:p.63																																																																																										(Sp): The oracle can alter a divination ability with a range of close, medium, or long to increase its range by 100%. An enlarged ability with a range of close now has a range of 50 ft. + 5 ft./level, while medium-range spells have a range of 200 ft. + 20 ft./level and long-range spells have a range of 800 ft. + 80 ft./level. Abilities whose ranges are not defined by distance, as well as abilities whose ranges are not close, medium, or long, do not have increased ranges. This alteration is made as a free action.
Maximize		KEY:Maximize ~ Oracle		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.SpellLike		SOURCEPAGE:p.63																																																																																										(Sp): All variable, numeric effects of all divination abilities are maximized. Saving throws and opposed rolls are not affected, nor are abilities without random variables. An empowered, maximized divination ability gains the separate benefits of each
