Divination Ability		KEY:Divination Ability					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.SpellLike																								(Sp): The oracle is able to use her divination abilities a limited number of times per day. The base daily divination allotment is given on Table 6-5: The Oracle. In addition, she receives bonus divinations per day if she has a high Charisma score. All divination abilities are an innate manifestation of the spell by the same name and do not require any material components other than the divination focus. The Difficulty Class for a saving throw against an oracle's divination is 10 + the divination ability level + the oracle's Wisdom modifier. An oracle is able to use any ability from the list without preparing it ahead of time.


